text: Abramovka () is a rural locality (a khutor) in Starostanichnoye Rural Settlement of Kamensky District, Rostov Oblast, Russia. The population was 790 as of 2010. There are 89 streets.Улицы хутора Абрамовка == References == Category:Rural localities in Rostov Oblast
title: Abramovka, Rostov Oblast
